# CODEOWNERS — automatic PR reviewer assignment.
#
# Place this file at one of:
#   .github/CODEOWNERS   (recommended)
#   CODEOWNERS           (repo root)
#   docs/CODEOWNERS
#
# Syntax: <path-pattern> <@user-or-team> [<@user-or-team> ...]
# Later matches override earlier ones, so put broad rules first.
#
# Owner: @elad-reznikov is the maintainer's GitHub handle (a member of the
#   deepfusionlabs org). Note: GitHub does NOT expand environment variables in
#   this file and silently ignores an owner that is not a real user/team with
#   repo access — so keep this handle in sync with the maintainer's actual login.
#
# Reference:
#   https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
* @elad-reznikov

# Examples (uncomment and adapt):
